Class PlacemarkTests

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opengis.cite.kml2.CommonFixture
      • org.opengis.cite.kml2.CommonFeatureTests
        • org.opengis.cite.kml2.c1.PlacemarkTests

  • public class PlacemarkTests
extends CommonFeatureTests
    Implements tests that apply to the kml:Placemark element. A Placemark is a feature that may have an associated geometry element (that substitutes for kml:AbstractGeometryGroup).
    See Also:
    "OGC 12-007r2: OGC KML 2.3, 9.14", "OGC 14-068r2: OGC KML 2.3 - Abstract Test Suite, Conformance Level 1"

        public void findPlacemarkElements()
